Below are details of all properties of `-- ds.hero` component.

-- site-doc.component-property: `title`
type: Caption (`required`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. It's used to add a
title to `hero` component.

-- site-doc.component-property: `body`
type: Caption (`required`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. It's used to add a
body to `hero` component.

-- site-doc.component-property: `tag`
type: Caption (`required`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. It's used to add a
tag to `hero` component.

-- site-doc.component-property: `designation`
type: Caption (`required`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. It's used to add a
designation of author to `hero` component.

-- site-doc.component-property: `avatar`
type: ftd.image-src (`required`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. Using `avatar`
attribute image can be added.

